        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-9d8d7758-8385-410b-95be-d4bca7680669" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
