<p class="">Will the right hon. Gentleman tell us one which was willing to go to war?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-3c8b601c-6573-4a47-abc4-53831f021cc9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
