<p class="">Is the hon. Gentleman aware that the Italian obligations under the Triple Alliance were not binding in any war that affected us?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-80ef2313-dc3e-4253-8de1-9d7579d79dfc" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
