<p class="">On a point of Order, Mr. Deputy-Speaker. This Debate is of first-class importance, and for the last hour and a half there has been no representative of the Government here. We have had short relays of subordinate officials, and I want to ask whether, in view of that fact and the importance of some of the speeches which have been delivered, of which, apparently, no record is kept for the Government's information, you will accept a Motion for the Adjournment?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
