<p class="">The hon. Member said in his pamphlet: <blockquote><q>" There are two international brigades in Spain, one a fighting force drawn from the Socialist movements of the world and the other an international cheka drawn from the Comintern's paid gangsters "</q></blockquote></p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-1ca677dc-30b6-44fd-b68c-e0eb9472763f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
