                Captain Cazalet
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-928397ec-d3bc-41e1-a7ca-b61307c3fbec" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-05-02/debates/ec43eba6-dec7-4322-9f21-631ed4941b29/Anglo-ItalianAgreement#contribution-928397ec-d3bc-41e1-a7ca-b61307c3fbec">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
