<p class="">Not at all. As the Prime Minister said, it is not grovelling on the part of a great country to extend the right hand of friendship to another country with which it has a quarrel, and to say, "Let us discuss our differences and our mutual grievances."</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
